This section provides an overview of how to install GlusterFS.

*GlusterFS Installation Overview*

1.  Check the Gluster 3.2: Understanding the GlusterFS License[
GlusterFS License].
2.  Verify that your system matches the minimum system requirements. For
more information, see
Gluster 3.2: Checking GlusterFS Minimum Requirements[ Checking Minimum
Requirements].
3.  Complete the installation procedure corresponding to your
environment. Refer to Gluster 3.2: Installing GlusterFS Server[
Installing GlusterFS Server] for more information.

